1. B U I L D   I N S T R U C T I O N S

2.1 Dependencies

  * libevent 2.0.x (http://libevent.org/) for handling socket events
  * xrootd > 3.1.0 (http://xrootd.org), for some base libraries
  * libreadline (http://www.gnu.org/s/readline/), for managing commandline
    (optional)

2.2 Build parameters

  The build process supports the following parameters:

  * XROOTD_DIR           - path where xrootd is installed
  * LIBEVENT_DIR         - path where lib event is installed
  * READLINE_ROOT_DIR    - path to the root of the readline installation if it
                           cannot be detected in a standard location
  * CMAKE_C_COMPILER     - path to the c compiler that should be used
  * CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER   - path to the c++ compiler that should be used

